      "side": 1,
      "message": "We don\u0027t have access to a Gitiles client at the point in the code where we call rebase, so it would require some plumbing.  Is it possible to determine whether a rebase is required based on the ChangeInfo alone?  The \"mergeable\" field seems like it would be the right thing to check, but the docs are unclear: https://gerrit-review.googlesource.com/Documentation/rest-api-changes.html#change-info",
      "parentUuid": "121972ba_4129b6d0",
      "revId": "77e230f70d3d5380512f546aff761d6875bfe2f2",
